{"lang": "zh_CN", "eventid": "act51side", "eventName": "人们，我们", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "PA-4", "avgTag": "行动后", "storyName": "一墙之隔", "storyInfo": "娜塔莉娅四处奔走，在一些人的帮助下，找到了支持巴普洛维奇的关键人物——特里波列夫公爵。她设法威胁了公爵，使他不得不停止对巴普洛维奇的援助。", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g12_deitygrypherburgmeeting", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“......之后，我对照名单，依次与各个学生见面。”", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“与索尼娅不同，他们被送到城墙边的办公室与我交谈，大多面带恐惧，什么都不敢说。”", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我受够了！仲裁人阁下，帝国的听证会怎能纵容如此荒谬的、针对一位清白贵族的侮辱？", "name": "急切的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他曾是陛下亲封的枢密官，如果事实真如娜塔莉娅描述的那样，他又怎么可能取得这样的殊荣？", "name": "急切的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "任谁都能听出来，这封信名为忏悔，实为诘难，我们不能再被谣言牵着走了。", "name": "急切的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "据我所知，现场还有一份——", "name": "急切的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_405_absin_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这位大人，无论您对巴普洛维奇大人的“管理艺术”抱有怎样的欣赏态度，都请不要因此就把娜塔莉娅亲笔写下的血泪称为谣言。", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#6$2"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您不能因为我们此刻都在温暖的厅堂中对话，就否认外面正有人因饥寒交迫而战栗。", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#6$2"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_405_absin_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "毕竟，依照您的想法，如果世上真有那么多苦难，乌萨斯怎么可能繁荣数百年呢？", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#7$2"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卓娅女士，注意你的措辞。听证会尊重你烈士子女的身份，出于信任和对公正的索求让你来辅助作证，不是让你来这里侮辱贵族的！", "name": "急切的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_405_absin_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "仲裁委员会明鉴，我分明是在维护一位真正的贵族，我决不容忍任何人轻率地用“谣言”去污蔑她。", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#6$2"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "荒谬——", "name": "急切的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安静！", "name": "仲裁人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卓娅女士，你的责任是代为陈述娜塔莉娅小姐的证词，事实判断是仲裁委员会才能做的。", "name": "仲裁人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......抱歉，仲裁人阁下。", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果诸位大人在意的是“忏悔”的部分，那么接下来就是了。", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "还请仲裁人阁下允许我继续。", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "记住，如果你继续试图对任何贵族的观点进行评判，那么我将不再允许你发言。", "name": "仲裁人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "继续吧。", "name": "仲裁人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>“当我回到城中，向他们的父母汇报情况时，有的家长会多留我一会儿，想要了解更多有关他们孩子的情况。”</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 330.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 720.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>“为了寻找缓解封锁区内境况的契机，我必须要试探谁能够提供更多的帮助。”</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 330.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 720.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>“于是，我挑选了几位家长私下见面，刻意渲染了学生们所处境况的窘迫与凄惨。”</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 330.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 720.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>“最终，我找到了一位独生子被押的贵族，而他迫不及待地将我引荐给了他的上司。”</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 330.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 720.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "72_g13_nobleroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......以上就是我在封锁区内的全部见闻，议员阁下。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若是继续坐视巴普洛维奇大人的行为，甚至继续放任他们使用大型武器，这一定会在不久后酿成无法挽回的惨剧。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜塔莉娅小姐，从你的表述来看，你似乎希望议会能公布巴普洛维奇的罪行，从而剥夺他的官秩，甚至将其撤职。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是希望能阻止他。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "议员阁下，请原谅我话语的直接。我对议会既无意评判，也产生不了影响，但我能想象这其中会有多大阻力。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那么，或许我们就应该答应他的要求，暂缓抛下封锁区地块的决议，然后他就会如约释放学生们。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你相信他会兑现承诺吗？", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不，我无法信任巴普洛维奇大人。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#3$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且我也明白，您之所以会这么问我，是因为您同样无法信任他。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2162_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，你很聪明，也许你和我的女儿会聊得来。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#2$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的下属也向我报告过，你从封锁区回来后并没有按照他的要求，煽动家长们一同想办法保留封锁区。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反之，你选择从家长们的身份、状况和性格入手，找到了我。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你认为我是能左右事情的关键，也是你目前能接触到的、最有政治影响力的对象。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的判断全都正确，我的想法，那些青涩的算计，在您面前一览无余。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是阁下，我只是无法不去想我的朋友们。就在我们交谈的时候，她们正在封锁区里遭受磨难，每一秒都有丧命的风险。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道您的顾虑，是源于我想法的不现实。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以阁下，我并不奢望能立即处罚巴普洛维奇大人，但至少我们应该争取改善封锁区内学生们的待遇，并解除封锁区的重型武装。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2162_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......很遗憾，当下的议会大概无法满足这些请求。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#3$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巴普洛维奇大人曾和我提到，他得到了议会当中许多贵族朋友的支持。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你恐怕说漏了一个“旧”字。或者说，“军事贵族”。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "开诚布公地说，乌萨斯贵族间的阵营对立，恐怕对玻利瓦尔人都谈不上是什么秘密了，你不必如此谨慎。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "由于近来的动乱，每一个决议，每一条规章，谁今天在议会上逞了口舌之快，谁明日被皇帝陛下夸奖，处处都是党同伐异，必分高低。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "仅是帝国议会，就有四百多名议员，他们大都家世显赫，功勋卓著。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "居住在圣骏堡的、姓氏被计入了《贵族谱系》的世袭贵族，有将近八百人。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至于那些有影响力的荣誉市民，更是不计其数......每个人的态度都很复杂。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2162_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果世事都像切薄饼一样能轻易分成两半......我想乌萨斯也不会走到现在这种局面。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#8$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是想告诉我......", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使是新贵族，其中也有人支持巴普洛维奇大人。现在之所以无法阻止他，也是因为他有许多有权势的支持者。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以即使是我，甚至是议长，都无法在这件事情上跨过众人的意见，给你们提供任何实质性的帮助。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能有幸与您交流，就已经是莫大的帮助了。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的目标不会改变，要真正解救索尼娅以及封锁区里的人们，就必须尽量干扰巴普洛维奇大人。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2162_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "判断不错，但只有判断是不够的。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#2$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在年轻的时候，人们很容易知道自己应该反对什么，却很难知道自己应该去做什么。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#2$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜塔莉娅小姐，你会怎么做呢？", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#2$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......如果我能调查清楚不同人支持他的原因，并且联系上一些潜在的“朋友”......", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#2$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您提醒过我，每一个人的态度都是复杂的。换种角度说，即使是旧贵族，即使曾经是他的盟友，也可能会在特定情况下态度发生偏移。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#8$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2162_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你把那句话看作是“提醒”，这可真是......", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#2$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等事情解决之后，请一定要再来坐坐。等阿洛达没在做她自己的事的时候吧，也许......", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#2$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您说什么？", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没什么。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜塔莉娅小姐，我这里有一个消息，是即使维特议长明令禁止，也已经在部分贵族中传播开来的。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "冬季舞会之后，出于一些原因，皇帝陛下没有返回宫殿。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "截至目前，议长暗中派人调查，却始终没有发现任何线索，排除到最后，就只剩下一个地方。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2162_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一个此时难以查证的地方。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#9$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "难以查证的地方？难道——", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#6$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的意思是，陛下或许在封锁区里......就连议长也没法实施搜查吗？", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2162_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以当下的局势来看，我们希望尽可能地低调处理，以免制造出更大的混乱。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#9$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而某些不知从何处得知陛下失踪消息的贵族，却似乎希望这个局面能够持续。这也与你告诉我的情况相吻合。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#9$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......一些利益交换、心照不宣的态度倾斜，又或是想趁机一劳永逸地解决压在他们头顶上最大的困难。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#9$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更不用说恰好在这时，那原本应该立即启用以保护陛下的特殊手段，也出于某些原因而反应迟滞。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#9$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，这个消息并不具有明确的时效性，甚至也不算难以打听。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#9$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "重要的是，在特殊手段生效之前，你可以继续按照你的方式去解决你朋友面临的问题。而如果特殊手段生效......", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#9$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2162_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的朋友们，大概就只能自求多福了。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#8$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......这个特殊手段，是指——", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#8$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2162_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你只需要知道，当它生效，陛下一定会安全地回到他的宫殿之中。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#9$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不过，我这里还有一件或许能宽慰你的事。维特议长已经按下了抛下封锁区的决议，这至少在一周之内都不会改变。", "name": "某位议员"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2162_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您所说的这些，对我们至关重要。我代表我自己，以及我的朋友，一同衷心地感谢您。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g12_deitygrypherburgmeeting", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......也就是说，有议员向娜塔莉娅小姐透露，某些新贵族希望陛下在封锁区里受到折磨，甚至遇害？", "name": "仲裁人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尽管听证会出于维护贵族尊严的考量，赞成隐去名字的做法，但请诸位放心，此后会对此进行详尽的调查。", "name": "仲裁人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，是谁？是谁已经丧心病狂到这个地步，我要求证人马上、立即公布那些禽兽的名字！", "name": "急切的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把他们从巢穴里挖出来，看看他们只为金钱跳动的心脏究竟长没长着乌萨斯人的血肉！", "name": "急切的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我并非娜塔莉娅本人，我对信函里提到的那些人的名字一无所知。", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不过从后文来看，她接下来寻访了不少历史悠久的贵族府邸，它们的主人似乎同样不太热情......当然，您也可以说他们是不为金钱所动。", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "急切的贵族", "content": "这、这太荒谬了，无论是谁都说出来，不然就是——"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "急切的贵族", "content": "拉我干什么？"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_slap"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他下意识地狠狠挥手，清脆的巴掌声再次驱散了听证会上难得的凝重，在场所有人好奇地看过去，刚才阻止他的同伴正捂着脸。"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同伴面对着众人的“关切”，只得对他们挤出一个僵硬的讪笑，但双眼却恶狠狠地瞟向急切而冒失的贵族，对方悻悻地合上了嘴巴。"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那，我还应该继续往下说吗？毕竟在这之后，有人给了娜塔莉娅一份军事贵族的名单，附在这封信件后。", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_405_absin_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "信上写着，这些贵族未经核验就咬定陛下失踪是谣言，还有人想通过娜塔莉娅趁机勒索那些孩子被抓的家长......", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#7$2"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尤其是在十二月二十九日下午，有一位不愿透露姓名的绅士向娜塔莉娅勒索——", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#7$2"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，你不能透露那些贵族的具体信息。", "name": "仲裁人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我会按照要求隐去他们的名字，也不会对他们的行为进行评判。", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......具体时间和地点特征也要规避，不要对我的实质要求故作不知。只说事情，只说事情本身，明白了吗？！", "name": "仲裁人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没有问题，阁下。", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在此之后，虽然娜塔莉娅确实赢得了一部分家长的支持，但最关键的是，她在某日登门拜访了一位重要的贵族人士。", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#1$2"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_405_absin_1#9$2"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他长期支持巴普洛维奇大人，并始终宣扬应对犯事学生实施重刑，只要——", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#9$2"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g7_reception", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#4$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您认同我们的想法，就能最大限度地降低封锁区内的交火烈度。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#4$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "罗斯托夫家的小姐......请回吧，若不是你放言事态危急，我本没有和切尔诺伯格的贵族打交道的想法。", "name": "某位公爵"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公爵阁下，此事关乎陛下安危，谁都承担不起让乌萨斯面临国难的罪责。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#9$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "国难？孩子，你或许不知道，这些年的圣骏堡，每天都有疯子高喊这个词——当然，我并不是在说你。", "name": "某位公爵"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "对于你口中那骇人听闻的消息，请原谅我不得不故作不知。毕竟我的理智在不断向我提醒——这又是那些暴发户自导自演的戏码。", "name": "某位公爵"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或许是我理解错了，但您似乎是在指责我们拿陛下的安危演戏，完全不担心危险发生的后果。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#3$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我只是不接受讹诈，即使你穿戴得齐整高贵，就像任何一个圣骏堡的贵族那样。", "name": "某位公爵"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在如今的乌萨斯，没有什么比教育那些思想中毒的年轻人更为重要。", "name": "某位公爵"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果说，在皇村——在萨列夫格勒区聚众闹事都不能严惩，乌萨斯还有什么威信可言？", "name": "某位公爵"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你关心同学的心情可以理解，我不会追究你为暴民辩护的罪责，今天的会面，就当没有发生过吧。", "name": "某位公爵"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我明白了，公爵阁下。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#4$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不过，请相信，您终有一天，也会起身为所谓的“暴民”辩护。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#4$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你说什么？", "name": "某位公爵"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_armycrowd", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我会找到您，是因为我从一些贵族那里听闻，您和您的继承人一直在私底下煽动学生。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#12$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2165_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人已经掌握了相关证据，能够证明公爵阁下府邸中的地下室，就是学生活动的据点，甚至拍摄到了他们就在您花园里排演的画面。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#3$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......呵，无谓的尝试。孩子，无论你再怎么虚张声势，我也不会上当。", "name": "某位公爵"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他缓缓起身，不再对上娜塔莉娅的目光。"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已经警告过你，如果试图讹诈——", "name": "某位公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2165_1#3$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "type": "cgitem", "id": "cgitem_72_i06_3", "from": 0.5, "to": 0.5}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 5.0, "type": "cg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "cgitem", "attributes": {"image": "cgitem_72_i06_3", "style": "cg", "pfrom": "80,0", "pto": "100,0", "pduration": 20.0, "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "aduration": 0.0, "layer": 2.0, "sfrom": 1.0, "sto": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "72_i06_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "y": 30.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"duration": 20.0, "block": "false", "xFrom": 50.0, "xTo": 30.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_sunlight_r", "layer": 1.0, "y": 200.0, "xto": 200.0, "yto": 200.0, "movetime": 30.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_sunlight_l", "layer": 2.0, "y": 200.0, "x": 250.0, "xto": 300.0, "yto": 200.0, "movetime": 30.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_armycrowd"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$m_avg_ursusdaily_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "听我的口令！队尾转队首，齐步撤退！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "据我所知，很早就有人猜测您的继承人与学生组织之间的关系，而您甚至为此威胁过她的老师们，要求禁止这类“谣言”传播。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可凑巧的是，自从冬季舞会那时参与示威的学生们被捕后，您的继承人就再也没有露面。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是因为她正在中部研学——", "name": "某位公爵"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您当然可以继续自欺欺人。只是，也许是我自作多情，想当然地认为自己与您有相似的立场，能够帮您挽回继承人的前程......", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，可怜的奥尔佳。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你、你做了什么？！", "name": "某位公爵"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就在这里，什么也没做。也许只是恰巧在您家里遇上了他们排练的时刻。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者说，连我这样的不速之客，都能无意间撞见他们的举动，恰恰说明这些学生在您府中的活跃程度，不是吗？", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你——", "name": "某位公爵"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_sunlight_r", "layer": 1.0, "y": 300.0, "x": 300.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_sunlight_l", "layer": 2.0, "y": 300.0, "x": 300.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "cgitem", "attributes": {"image": "cgitem_72_i06_3", "style": "cg", "layer": 2.0, "sfrom": 1.0, "sto": 0.85, "sduration": 30.0, "pfrom": "100,10", "pto": "90,0", "pduration": 30.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 10.0, "type": "cgitem", "id": "cgitem_72_i06_3", "from": 0.5, "to": 0.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xTo": 0.0, "duration": 30.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 30.0, "type": "cg", "from": 0.0, "to": 0.5}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "cgitem", "attributes": {"image": "cgitem_72_i06_1", "style": "cg", "layer": 1.0, "sfrom": 0.85, "sto": 1.0, "sduration": 30.0, "pfrom": "-530,100", "pto": "-430,0", "pduration": 30.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "cgitem", "attributes": {"image": "cgitem_72_i06_2", "style": "cg", "layer": 3.0, "sfrom": 0.85, "sto": 1.0, "sduration": 30.0, "pfrom": "570,100", "pto": "470,0", "pduration": 30.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "窗外阳光炫目，早露垂下眼睛，以无法让人察觉的幅度点了点头，旋即换上了属于贵族小姐的礼貌笑容。"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如我所说，我只是听到了一些传闻。对公爵阁下而言，幸运的是，它们并没有扩散。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你想要什么？", "name": "某位公爵"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是我想要什么，是您需要守护自己，和整个家族的未来。", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "现在刚过正午，希望您能允许我在此稍作休息，静候您的答复——", "name": "早露"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "hidecgitem", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g12_deitygrypherburgmeeting", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不是这样的！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这是谎言......仲裁人阁下！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特里波列夫公爵？", "name": "仲裁人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2171_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我坦白，娜塔莉娅·罗斯托娃找到的人是我，我也的确同意了削减巴普洛维奇军备的要求。", "name": "特里波列夫公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2171_1#1$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我的女儿是无罪的！她是被他们、被这群学生组织的疯子胁迫的！", "name": "特里波列夫公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2171_1#1$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她会在今天出席作证，勇敢地证明自己的清白，揭露娜塔莉娅的谎言。她就是下一个证人。", "name": "特里波列夫公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2171_1#1$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_405_absin_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公爵大人，娜塔莉娅的这封信，忏悔的便是对您、对其他人的不诚实。", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#6$2"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "乌萨斯从来没有给过我们机会，而从始至终，娜塔莉娅也没有背叛任何人，她只是做出了正确的选择，保护了应当保护的朋友。", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#6$2"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "无论谁出面，在这里发表任何搬弄是非的证词，她都无愧于乌萨斯，无愧于我们。", "name": "苦艾"}, "figure_art": "avg_405_absin_1#6$2"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2171_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你——", "name": "特里波列夫公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2171_1#1$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$gavel1"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "肃静！", "name": "仲裁人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "临时休会十分钟。", "name": "仲裁人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "书记官，让下一位证人做好准备......", "name": "仲裁人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2168_1#1$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_peoplestandup"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沃伦佐娃夫人......我不明白，这不像您的作风。", "name": "急切的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您明明拿到了娜塔莉娅真正的证词，如果能够与卓娅的说法对峙，至少不会让列位贵族如此失态。", "name": "急切的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可您从她讲述封锁区的遭遇开始就沉默不语，有好几位大人都在看着您，愤怒溢于言表。", "name": "急切的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您到底在等什么？", "name": "急切的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "72_g13_nobleroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$wasteland_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......如您所愿。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，好。这样，我就还来得及对你的父母有所交代。一切都还来得及。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瞧瞧，真是漂亮的字迹啊，娜塔申卡。让我看看你有没有遗漏——", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......娜塔申卡，你......", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你写的这些，都是什么呀？这不是“忏悔信”吗？", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，忏悔信。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#15$1"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我忏悔，向所有曾受我的诡计蒙骗的人，和所有被这些人利用并抛弃的、受难的学生。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#15$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他们都曾是我的同学，即使我们从未就读于同一所学校。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我们也都是乌萨斯人，我们本该拥有同样的命运。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不！", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子，我的孩子！是谁要让你背负这样的痛苦？是谁指责你将他们欺骗？这不是我想让你做的，这绝不是！", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天哪，玛尔莎，我......我该怎么办？我该怎么做才能宽慰你可怜的孩子？不要说这样恐怖的话了，娜塔申卡，这不是你的错！", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可总有人应该为此付出代价，或背负罪责，夫人。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我写下这些，按照您的要求描述这些人的参与，以及......我所知道的故事。您却说，这不是我应该做的。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "难道我剖开自己的做法不对吗？还是说我应该永远对责任敬而远之，就像个永远长不大的孩子？", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我们面前，你们永远都只是孩子！我也只是想帮助你，像帮助任何一个朋友的亲人——甚至像帮助自己的孩子。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不过是些荒唐的、尽可以被原谅的错误，谁需要这样沉重的忏悔？我决不愿看你自苦至此，我的......娜塔申卡......", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白，夫人，我都明白。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的热情，您的真挚，甚至常常达到使我在相处中觉得煎熬的程度。可这并不是您的问题。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是我自己，在这些日子接触到太多以往遥不可及的高贵之人后，在亲身了解了他们的所思所想和对乌萨斯的感情后，总忍不住去想——", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#3$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "骏鹰王国尚未灭亡的时候，如今的乌萨斯贵族们的祖先，也都是一个个普通人，就连伊戈尔大帝也只是军旅行伍中的一员。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在骏鹰挥动着鞭子的时候，他们毫无畏惧地冲了上去，挡在被奴役者的身前。这才让大家相信，他们拥有荣耀的、勇者的血脉。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但若是有一天，这些流淌着勇者血液的人，选择将另一些被压迫和被侮辱的人踩在脚下，甚至拿起了骏鹰曾挥动的鞭子......", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#12$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#15$1"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "还会有人相信他们，甘愿与他们为伍吗？", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#15$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我，竟然也要加入，作为其中的一员吗？", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#9$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这是......我们与生俱来的权利——", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜塔申卡，不......", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，夫人，只有这一次，请容我拒绝。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果说，有什么权利是我希望所有人都能与生俱来的，那一定是......", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“选择权”。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#5$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而现在，正如您所说......“一切都还来得及”。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "来得及让我做出选择，来得及让我决定背负。", "name": "早露"}, "figure_art": "avg_197_poca_1#4$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g12_deitygrypherburgmeeting", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......只是，没有必要。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“再怎么精心编造的谎言，也敌不过切身经历的事实”。娜塔申卡......只是做出了选择。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可她蒙骗了您，至少要让她付出代价——", "name": "急切的贵族"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大人，我感谢您的热心，只不过......", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已经有些累了。", "name": "沃伦佐娃夫人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2173_1#1$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "hidecgitem", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}